title: Sign, But No Trade
description:
Pablo Torre, Domonique Foxworth and David Jacoby debate what it tells them about the 49ers QB situation that they are bringing back Jimmy Garoppolo and how New York signing RJ Barrett impacts trade talks for Donovan Mitchell.
